#### Easily connect your Frosting shop to Stripe to start accepting payments.

### Step 1  

Hover over the **User** icon on the top menu bar.  Click on **Shop Manager**

![Shop Manager Top Bar](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Menu+%3E+Click+Shop+Manager.png =650x)

## Step 2  

From the Shop Manager, click on **Settings**.

![Hover Settings](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings.png =500x)

## Step 3  

Click on **Payment**.

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png =500x)

## Step 4  

Click on the **Connect with Stripe** button.

![Click Connect with Stripe](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe.png =550x)

## Step 5  

You will be taken to Stripe to create or to log in to an existing account.

#### Create an account  

Once you have filled out all of the details, click **Authorize access to this Account** and you will be connected to Frosting and will be able to accept payments!

![Stripe Authorize access to this account](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe+-+Authorize+Account.png =550x)

#### Login to an existing account  

If you already have an account you can click on **Sign in**.

![Stripe Login](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe+-+Sign+Into+Stripe+Account.png =550x)

## Step 6

Click on **Payment**.

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png)

## Step 7

Click on **Payment**.

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png)
